December 1st the “SOLEZ” Believe In You, Pre - Order drops for the public to purchase. Made this shoe for all the people that have been told they can’t or won’t be able to do what they want to do In life. I remember back in middle / highschool I was getting suspended for looking at sneakers on the computers during class instead of doing my “work”. Now I’m releasing my own sneaker to the world that I designed for “work”. Life is a crazy place and long as you work hard, never give up & believe in you, anything is possible ❤️‍🔥
